title: Neff Carol Contest
description: Mr. Neff challenges you to create your own Neff X-Mas Carol. So grab your video cameras and upload your Neff X-Mas Carol videos to YouTube and send the link to info@neffheadwear.com. Winners will be selected December 25th 2011.
